  "time_ut": 1657022921,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bcb\u0ba9\u0bbe \u0b85\u0baa\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bae\u0bcd: 4\u0b86\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc2\u0b9a\u0bbf \u0b85\u0bb5\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Corona risk: 4th vaccine is essential",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Director General of Health Services, Dr. Asela Gunawardena, has said that the public should get all 4 vaccines against the corona virus as there is a risk that the number of people infected with the corona virus will increase again in the country."
      ],
